sk.stu.fiit.league

Class League

  • java.lang.Object
    • sk.stu.fiit.league.League
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class League
extends Object
implements Serializable
    Class League represent a group of teams playing a sport who take part in competitions between each other. The league has entered basic information, such as start and end date, name, genre, maximum number of teams in the league, number of teams in the match, logo and description. Each league has its LeagueInfoWindow, a list of participating Teams, list of Matches that will take place and a list of Prizes for the best teams.
    See Also:
    LeagueOrganizer, Team, Match, Prize, Serialized Form
